{"word":"G2632 - κατακρίνω - katakrínō - kat-ak-ree'-no - Condemn","slug":"G2632","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κατακρίνω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>katakrínō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>kat-ak-ree'-no"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Condemn"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"- Original: <b><el>κατακρίνω</el></b> <p />- Transliteration: <b>Katakrino</b> <p />- Phonetic: <b>kat-ak-ree'-no</b> <p class=\"def\">- Definition: </p> <p class='li260'><b>1.</b> to give judgment against, to judge worthy of punishment </p> <p class='li520'><b>a.</b> to condemn </p> <p class='li520'><b>b.</b> by one's good example to render another's wickedness the more evident and censurable </p> <p class=\"origin\"/>- Origin: from <a href=\"#/G2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a> <p />- TDNT entry: 18:51,5 <p />- Part(s) of speech: Verb <p />- Strong's: From <a href=\"#/G2596\">G2596</a> and <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>; to <i>judge against</i> that is <b><i>sentence</i></b>: - condemn damn. "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1252\">G1252</a>, <a href=\"#/G1253\">G1253</a>, <a href=\"#/G1469\">G1469</a>, <a href=\"#/G178\">G178</a>, <a href=\"#/G2631\">G2631</a>, <a href=\"#/G2633\">G2633</a>, <a href=\"#/G2917\">G2917</a>, <a href=\"#/G2919\">G2919</a>, <a href=\"#/G2920\">G2920</a>, <a href=\"#/G2922\">G2922</a>, <a href=\"#/G2923\">G2923</a>, <a href=\"#/G2924\">G2924</a>, <a href=\"#/G350\">G350</a>, <a href=\"#/G351\">G351</a>, <a href=\"#/G470\">G470</a>, <a href=\"#/G610\">G610</a>, <a href=\"#/G611\">G611</a>, <a href=\"#/G612\">G612</a>, <a href=\"#/G843\">G843</a>, <a href=\"#/G87\">G87</a>"}]}